Lorenz , Professor 247 Mechanical Engineering Building 1513 University Avenue Madison, WI  53706-1572 Tel: 608-262-5343 Fax: 608-265-2316 E-mail: lorenz@engr.wisc.edu The Wisconsin Manufacturing Automation and Robotics Consortium (WMARC) was established in 1984 to formalize, coordinate and enhance industry/university interactions in manufacturing automation and robotics.
